  "help.about": "Mayelana",
  "help.about_body": "I-ScanIQ iyi-tracker yamakhalori nokudla okunomsoco eyenza kube lula ukungena ngemvume ukudla kwakho ngokusebenzisa ukuskena kwesithombe. I-ScanIQ iwumkhiqizo we-Kinetex Intelligens, eyakhelwe ukukusiza ufinyelele izinjongo zakho zezempilo.",
