  "help.faq_q1": "Ngiskena kanjani ukudla?",
  "help.faq_a1": "Thepha inkinobho enkulu eskena ewolu emazansi esikrini. Thatha isithombe sokudla kwakho bese uhlelo lokusebenza luhlaziya amakhalori nezakhamzimba ngokuzenzakalelayo. Imiphumela yizilinganiso.",
  "help.faq_q2": "Ingabe idatha yami iyimfihlo?",
  "help.faq_a2": "Yebo. Silandela i-GDPR. Idatha yakho igcinwa ngokuphepha, ayindaliwe, futhi ungakwazi ukususa i-akhawunti yakho nganoma yisiphi isikhathi.",
  "help.faq_q3": "Ngithuthukisela kanjani ku-Premium?",
  "help.faq_a3": "Yiya kuphrofayela → Bhalisela i-Premium. I-Premium ikunikeza ukuskena okungenamkhawulo, iziphakamiso zokudla ze-AI nezibalo ezithuthukile. Ukubhalisa kucutshungulwa yi-Apple App Store ne-Google Play.",
  "help.faq_q4": "Inembile kangakanani iskena?",
  "help.faq_a4": "Isikena sinikeza izilinganiso ezinhle zokudla okuvamile, kodwa imiphumela yizilinganiso futhi ingahluka. Ungakwazi njalo ukulungisa usayizi wengxenye nokudla okunomsoco ngesandla ngemuva kokuskena.",
  "help.faq_q5": "Ingabe i-ScanIQ iseluleko sezokwelapha?",
  "help.faq_a5": "Cha. I-ScanIQ akuyona iseluleko sezokwelapha futhi ayithathi indawo yokubonisana nodokotela noma isazi sokudla. Khuluma nochwepheshe bezempilo ngaphambi kokwenza izinguquko ezinkulu ekudleni kwakho noma ekuzilolongeni.",
  "help.faq_q6": "Ngingasisebenzisa uhlelo lokusebenza ngaphandle kwe-intanethi?",
  "help.faq_a6": "Izici eziningi zidinga i-intanethi ngoba ukuskena kwe-AI nokuvumelanisa kusebenza efwini.",
