  "help.faq_q4": "Ichane kangakanani iskena?",
  "help.faq_a4": "Isikena sinika ukuqikelela okuhle kokutya okuqhelekileyo, kodwa iziphumo zizinto zokuqikelela kwaye zingahluka. Ungasoloko ulungisa ubungakanani besabelo kunye nezondlo ngesandla emva kokuskena.",
