  "help.faq_q1": "Ndinoongorora sei chikafu?",
  "help.faq_a1": "Ndapota dzvanya bhatani guru rekuongorora pasi pechidzitiro. Tora mufananidzo wekudya kwako uye app ichaongorora ma koriyori nezvikafu otomatiki. Mhedzisiro inofungidzirwa.",
  "help.faq_q2": "Data rangu rakaomarara here?",
  "help.faq_a2": "Hongu. Tiri kutevedzera GDPR. Data rako rinochengetwa zvakachena, haritombo tengeswa, uye unogona kubvisa akaunti yako chero nguva.",
  "help.faq_q3": "Ndinoita sei kuti ndikwidze kuPremium?",
  "help.faq_a3": "Enda kuProfile -> Enda kuPremium. Premium inokupa ma scan asina muganho, AI zano rekudya uye ongororo yepamusoro. Kunyoreswa kunogadziriswa neApple App Store uye Google Play.",
  "help.faq_q4": "Kuongorora kwakarurama sei?",
  "help.faq_a4": "Chishandiso chekuongorora chinopa fungidziro dzakanaka dzezvikafu zvakajairika, asi mhedzisiro inofungidzirwa uye inogona kusiyana. Unogona kugara uchigadzirisa huwandu hwechikafu uye zvikafu nemaoko mushure mekuongorora.",
  "help.faq_q5": "ScanIQ chipangamazano chekurapa here?",
  "help.faq_a5": "Kwete. ScanIQ hachisi chipangamazano chekurapa uye hachitsivi kubvunzana nachiremba kana nyanzvi yezvekudya. Taura nenyanzvi yehutano usati wachinja zvakakura pakudya kana kudzidziswa kwako.",
  "help.faq_q6": "Ndine chokwadi chekushandisa app offline here?",
  "help.faq_a6": "Zvizhinji zvezvinhu zvinoda internet nekuti AI scanning uye sync zvinomhanya mugore.",
