  "help.disclaimer_body": "ScanIQ siupangiri wazachipatala ndipo sichilowa m'malo mwa dokotala kapena katswiri wazakudya. Ma calories ndi zakudya zimangoyerekezera ndipo zitha kukhala zolakwika. Lankhulani ndi akatswiri a zaumoyo musanasinthe kwambiri zakudya zanu kapena zolimbitsa thupi.",
