  "help.about": "About",
  "help.about_body": "ScanIQ ndi tracker ya makalori ndi zakudya zomwe zimathandiza kwambiri kulemba zakudya zanu kudzera pa kujambula zithunzi. ScanIQ ndi chinthu cha Kinetex Intelligens, chomwe chinapangidwa kuti akuthandizeni kukwaniritsa zolinga zanu za thanzi.",
