  "help.faq_q1": "Kodi ndimajambula bwanji chakudya?",
  "help.faq_a1": "Dinani batani lalikulu loyenera la kujambula pansi pazenera. Jambulani chithunzi cha chakudya chanu ndipo pulogalamu idzawonetsa ma calories ndi zakudya zokha. Zotsatira zimangoyerekeza.",
  "help.faq_q2": "Kodi deta yanga ndi yachinsinsi?",
  "help.faq_a2": "Inde. Timatsatira GDPR. Deta yanu imasungidwa mosatetezedwa, siyigulitsidwa konse, ndipo mutha kuchotsa akaunti yanu nthawi iliyonse.",
  "help.faq_q3": "Kodi ndimakweza bwanji ku Premium?",
  "help.faq_a3": "Pitani ku Mbiri → Pitani ku Premium. Premium imakupatsani mwayi wosawerengeka wojambula, malingaliro a chakudya cha AI komanso kuunika kwakukulu. Zolembetsa zimakonzedwa ndi Apple App Store ndi Google Play.",
  "help.faq_q4": "Kodi kujambula kumakhala kolondola bwanji?",
  "help.faq_a4": "Chosakanizira chimapereka ziwerengero zabwino za zakudya zomwe zimagwiritsidwa ntchito nthawi zambiri, koma zotsatira zimangoyerekeza ndipo zitha kusiyana. Mutha kusintha kukula kwa chakudya ndi zakudya pamanja mukatha kujambula.",
  "help.faq_q5": "Kodi ScanIQ ndi upangiri wa zamankhwala?",
  "help.faq_a5": "Ayi. ScanIQ si upangiri wa zamankhwala ndipo sichilowa m'malo mwa dokotala kapena katswiri wa zakudya. Lankhulani ndi akatswiri a zaumoyo musanasinthe kwambiri zakudya zanu kapena maphunziro anu.",
  "help.faq_q6": "Kodi ndingagwiritsire ntchito pulogalamuyi popanda intaneti?",
  "help.faq_a6": "Zinthu zambiri zimafuna intaneti chifukwa kujambula kwa AI ndi kugwirizanitsa kumayenda mu mtambo.",
