  "help.title": "Āwhina",
  "help.disclaimer": "Whakakahore Hauora",
  "help.disclaimer_body": "Ehara a ScanIQ i te tohutohu hauora, ā, kāore hoki e whakakapi i te kōrero ki te tākuta, ki te kaiwhakamānu rānei. He whakatau tata ngā kaara me te kai tōtika, ā, he hē pea. Kōrero ki te tohunga hauora i mua i te panoni nui ki tō kai, ki tō mahi korikori rānei.",
