  "help.faq_q1": "Me pēhea te karapa kai?",
  "help.faq_a1": "Patohia te pātene karapa karaka nui kei raro o te mata. Tangohia he whakaahua o tō kai, ā, ka tātari aunoatia e te taupānga ngā kaara me ngā matūkai. He whakatau tata ngā hua.",
  "help.faq_q2": "He tūmataiti aku raraunga?",
  "help.faq_a2": "Āe. E whai ana mātou i te GDPR. Kei te rongoatia ō raraunga kia haumaru, kāore rawa e hokona, ā, ka taea e koe te muku i tō pūkete i ngā wā katoa.",
  "help.faq_q3": "Me pēhea Au te Whakapai ake ki Premium?",
  "help.faq_a3": "Haere ki Profile → Go Premium. Ka hoatu e Premium ki a koe ngā karapa mutunga kore, ngā whakaaro kai AI me ngā tātari matatau. Ka mahia ngā ohauru e Apple App Store me Google Play.",
  "help.faq_q4": "He pēhea te tika o te karapa?",
  "help.faq_a4": "Ka hoatu e te matawai ngā whakatau tata pai mō ngā kai noa, engari he whakatau tata ngā hua, ā, ka rerekē. Ka taea e koe te whakatika i te rahi o te wāhanga me te kai tōtika ā-ringa i muri i te karapa.",
  "help.faq_q5": "He tohutohu hauora a ScanIQ?",
  "help.faq_a5": "Kāo. Ehara a ScanIQ i te tohutohu hauora, ā, kāore e whakakapi i te kōrero ki te tākuta, ki te kaiwhakamānu rānei. Kōrero ki te tohunga hauora i mua i te panoni nui ki tō kai, ki tō whakangungu rānei.",
  "help.faq_q6": "Ka taea e au te whakamahi i te taupānga tuimotu?",
  "help.faq_a6": "Me whai ipurangi te nuinga o ngā āhuatanga nā te mea kei te kapua te matawai AI me te tukutahi.",
