  "help.title": "Kōkua",
  "help.disclaimer": "Hoʻolaha Ola",
  "help.disclaimer_body": "ʻAʻole ʻōlelo aʻoaʻo olakino ʻo ScanIQ a ʻaʻole hoʻololi i ke kūkākūkā ʻana me ke kauka a i ʻole ka meaʻai. He kuhi wale nā calorie a me ka meaʻai a he hewa paha. E kamaʻilio me kekahi ʻoihana mālama ola ma mua o ka hoʻololi nui ʻana i kāu meaʻai a i ʻole ka hoʻomaʻamaʻa.",
