  "help.faq_q1": "Pehea wau e scan ai i ka meaʻai?",
  "help.faq_a1": "E paʻi i ke pihi scan ʻalani nui ma lalo o ka pale. E kiʻi i ke kiʻi o kāu meaʻai a e nānā ʻakomi ka app i nā calorie a me nā meaʻai. He kuhi wale nā hopena.",
  "help.faq_q2": "Malū paha kaʻu ʻikepili?",
  "help.faq_a2": "ʻAe. Mālama mākou i ka GDPR. Mālama paʻa ʻia kāu ʻikepili, ʻaʻole kūʻai ʻia, a hiki iā ʻoe ke holoi i kāu moʻokāki i kēlā me kēia manawa.",
  "help.faq_q3": "Pehea wau e hoʻonui ai i ka Premium?",
  "help.faq_a3": "E hele i ka Profile → E hele i Premium. Hāʻawi ʻo Premium iā ʻoe i nā scan palena ʻole, nā manaʻo meaʻai AI a me nā analytics kiʻekiʻe. Mālama ʻia nā kau inoa e Apple App Store a me Google Play.",
  "help.faq_q4": "Pehea ka pololei o ka scan?",
  "help.faq_a4": "Hāʻawi ka scanner i nā kuhi maikaʻi no nā meaʻai maʻamau, akā he kuhi wale nā hopena a hiki ke ʻokoʻa. Hiki iā ʻoe ke hoʻololi i ka nui o ka ʻāpana a me ka meaʻai ma hope o ka scan ʻana.",
  "help.faq_q5": "He ʻōlelo aʻoaʻo olakino anei ʻo ScanIQ?",
  "help.faq_a5": "ʻAʻole. ʻAʻole ʻōlelo aʻoaʻo olakino ʻo ScanIQ a ʻaʻole pani i ke kūkākūkā ʻana me ke kauka a i ʻole ka meaʻai. E kamaʻilio me kekahi ʻoihana mālama ola ma mua o ka hoʻololi nui ʻana i kāu meaʻai a i ʻole ka hoʻomaʻamaʻa.",
  "help.faq_q6": "Hiki iaʻu ke hoʻohana i ka app ma waho pūnaewele?",
  "help.faq_a6": "Pono ka hapa nui o nā hiʻohiʻona i ka pūnaewele no ka mea ke holo nei ka scan AI a me ka sync ma ke ao.",
